{"tid":2050078,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"六四out了，六一二in了？ - 林夕","createTime":"2020-06-04T01:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T04:54:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f8079463eb5126afe2906e2fed5a5607b44171","tid":2050078,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T01:35:45.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%95/daily/article/20200604/20930243/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25A4%2595%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200604%2F20930243%2F&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraYzaf%2B7McJKZiP%2F5rhSwlYLA%3D&h=55183784\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25A4%2595%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200604%2F20930243%2F&h=1735b0fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%95/daily/article/20200604/20930243/</a><br />\n<br />\n六四out了，六一二in了？ - 林夕<br />\n<br />\n歷史對一些人是債務，利息幾代人也償還不清。難怪董建華要香港再出發，不放下六四這個包袱，就不能到達──大灣區？不能踏上國內金融中心之路？<br />\n<br />\n聯合聲明也不過是一張歷史文件，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n全球只有香港人三十年來堅持搞紀念晚會，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我模擬答案如下：。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其實，他們怕什麼？。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n早前跟黃耀明通電話，提起去年寫《回憶有罪》，好像是就是幾星期前的事。若《皇。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n黃耀明就在六月三號晚在網路上繼續背這個包袱，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼還要記住六四？正如我們會記住八三一，七二一，當中的關連，迂迴曲折驚險過海洋公園的過山車，若我們沒能力討回公道，起碼要寫下各自見證的故事，這大概是歷史其中一個悲涼的意義。<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>若我們記住歷史，歷史也不會遺忘我們。 </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n林夕<br />\n電郵 :linxiapple@gmail.com"},{"pid":"a448bd1f1160055a9a3dd1562fdc21a42a2c5b10","tid":2050078,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T01:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UASSMEQ5NEQ62DSTACK7H73SDE